Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,T-t-t-this is just\Nsloppy craftsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, sure is really especially\Nbeautiful out there today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's almost unbelievable,\Nisn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.15,0:00:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something about the air
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and just the way the sunshine is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.11,0:00:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sure, buddy. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. B-Brilliant. Very convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha... convincing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.87,0:00:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Responsive, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In real time. I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.41,0:00:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhh... okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.08,0:00:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.33,0:00:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Morty, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.75,0:00:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going to work. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.34,0:01:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what's with mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're saying that\Nshe's acting weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How sophisticated.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.63,0:01:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna burn out\Nthe cpu with this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.51,0:01:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you know what, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.80,0:01:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're acting weird, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.97,0:01:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever, quote-unquote "morty."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.81,0:01:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.06,0:01:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! Oof! Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.23,0:01:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right. I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.82,0:01:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, who can tell\Nme what 5 x 9 is?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.78,0:01:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.70,0:01:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.66,0:01:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What is 5 x 9?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... you know,\Nit's uhh ...At least 40.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.25,0:01:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Morty, that's exactly correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.54,0:01:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,5 x 9 is at least 40!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.13,0:01:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Come up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo! Way to go, morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody,\Nthis is the best student.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.96,0:01:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to be\Nthe teacher today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.97,0:01:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach us, morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.43,0:01:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,W-W-W—what do you\Nwant me to teach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.14,0:01:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you make\Nconcentrated dark matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.10,0:01:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.35,0:01:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Concentrated huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Concentrated dark matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.98,0:02:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The fuel for accelerated\Nspace travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, do you know how to make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.61,0:02:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Jessica: Come on, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.61,0:02:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't your grandpa,\Nlike, a scientist?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, but, you know,\Nhe told me that I shouldn't go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.49,0:02:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,around spouting off about, you\Nknow, his science and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you've seen him make\Nconcentrated dark matter a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, if you tell us,\NI'll be your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.54,0:02:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, y-you will?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.71,0:02:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like a rare opportunity,\Nmorty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Morty, u-uh, come on.\NThere's a family emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If he leaves,\NI'm giving him an "f."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rick: He doesn't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.34,0:02:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Rick, I have to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.80,0:02:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I was about\Nto get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.26,0:02:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Take a shower with me,\Nmorty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.43,0:02:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.35,0:02:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.64,0:02:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your clothes off and\Nget in the shower right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Y—y-y-you got to\Ntrust me, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.31,0:02:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get an\N"f" in class, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.73,0:02:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Morty, that's not class.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.94,0:02:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,T-t-t-that wasn't your teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't your school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This entire world\Nis not the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're inside a huge simulation\Nchamber on an alien spaceship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all fake morty...\NAll of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.99,0:02:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanobotic renderings, a bunch\Nof crazy fake nonsense, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.83,0:03:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't say so until\Nwe got in the shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't monitor us in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Monitor us?! W-Who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Zigerion scammers, morty —-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the galaxy's most ambitious,\Nleast successful con artists.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's lucky for\Nus they're also really
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,uncomfortable with nudity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.51,0:03:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, come on, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.76,0:03:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If everyone's just\Ngonna be insane today,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,at least let me be\Ninsane with Jessica.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let you do that, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,G-G-Give it! No, Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.57,0:03:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, god, sir!\NThey're still naked!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, check every five quintons\Nand tell me when they're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we should\Nmake kev/n look, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,W-W-Why would you even say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sir, we have\Na situation over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's a wiener on that\Nmonitor,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.79,0:03:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear to god, stu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Something is drawing a\Nlot of processing power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait. No wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's another real\Nhuman in the simulator.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Jerry...\NBig pitch meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Make-or-break rime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:03:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:03:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How did this happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the\Nabductions department?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, man, abductions just\Nfollows the acquisition order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't put this on acquisitions!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We only acquire humans that\Nhaven'tbeen simulated!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, simulations doesn't\Nsimulate anybody that's been
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,abducted, so oh, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh! It was no one's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.\NWell, then, problem solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait... no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still another\Nhuman in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Rick's son-in-law, Jerry Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.08,0:04:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So far, he hasn't noticed\Nhe's in a simulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.04,0:04:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, cap his sector at 5%\Nprocessing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,keep his settings on auto, and\Nwe'll deal with him later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Rick Sanchez is the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.51,0:04:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Got to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.59,0:04:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a pitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Got to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Ean'h radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, here 's... humah music.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Human music.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhp, uhp, uhp!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Morty, keep your hands\Noff your ding—dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only way\Nwe can speak freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Look around you, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think\Nthis world is real?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd have to be an idiot not to\Nnotice all the sloppy details.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Look —- that guy's putting\Na bun between two hot dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Morty: I don't know, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I've seen people\Ndo that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.14,0:05:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Rick:\NWell, look at that old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.47,0:05:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She's... she's walking\Na cat on a leash.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Mrs. Spencer does\Nthat all the time, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I-I-I don't want to\Nhear about Mrs. Spencer, morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She's an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, all right, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What about that, morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.98,0:05:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Morty:\NOkay, okay, you got me on that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really, morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you haven't\Nseen that somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,in real life before?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. I haven't seen that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, why would a\Npop tart want to live inside
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,a toaster, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that would be, like, the\Nscariest place for them to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're missing the point, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would he drive a smaller\Ntoaster with wheels?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, does your car look like\Na smaller version of your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why are they doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What do they want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that would be\Nobvious to you, morty,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,if you'd been paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We got the president of the\NUnited States in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We need 1000 of concentrated\Ndark matter, stat, or he'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Concentrated dark matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They were asking\Nabout that in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.77,0:06:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a special fuel I\Ninvented to travel through
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,space faster than anybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,These zigerions are always\Ntrying to scam me out of my secrets,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but they made a big\Nmistake this time, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They dragged you into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.99,0:06:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now they're gonna pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you...\NW-W-What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll scam the scammers, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're gonna take them for\Neverything they've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Jerry:\NNational apple farmers of america,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,welcome to our ad agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Jerry Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just... get to the pitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, simple question, gentlemen,\NWhat are apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.01,0:06:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.35,0:06:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What are apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Apples are food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And... when do we need food?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,When we're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:07:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,With that, I give\Nyou your new slogan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All: Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So... I sold it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I sold the idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.12,0:07:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All: Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my god! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Together: Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I just sold my first pitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.26,0:07:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Slow down! Lookin' good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.47,0:07:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess who just sold\Nthe apples campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Who just sold\Nthe apples campaign?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it wasn't a rip—off\Nof "got milk?" After all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess someone was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.78,0:07:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, all is forgiven,\Nbecause right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got an erection the size\Nof an east coast lighthouse,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm coming home to share\Nit with my beautiful wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! See you in 10 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make\Nlove to my wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:07:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Lookin' good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.46,0:07:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Slow down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, geez, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.09,0:08:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know if I\Nlike this plan, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, crowds,\Nt-t—t—they have a tendency
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to make me really nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Morty, relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a bunch\Nof 1s and os out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.06,0:08:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just follow my lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.31,0:08:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, deejay, drop that beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This crowd looks too small for\None of ourfamous rap concerts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think we can\Nperform our new song,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,"the recipe for\Nconcentrated dark matter,"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,for a crowd this tiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You got that right, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.79,0:08:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Rick: Now that's more like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Morty, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me hear everybody\Nsay "hey—oh!" Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.63,0:08:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All the ladies say, "yeah!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.09,0:08:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody over 30,\Ndo this with your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.34,0:08:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody with a red shirt,\Njump up and down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm. Mm. Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm, mm, mm, mm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.45,0:09:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, everyone whose first name\Nbegins with an "I"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,who isn't hispanic, walk in a\Ncircle the same number of times
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,as the square root\Nof your age times 10!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Before the system reboots!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Jerry: Yeah! You like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now who's unremarkable?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You hungry for apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.59,0:09:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hungry... for... apples?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the best sex\NI've ever had in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... it's... too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't deserve this, Beth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a fraud.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man, Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,W-w-w-where we running to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the simulation, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.74,0:09:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, the chamber\Noperates like a treadmill,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,with the virtual world\Ndisappearing behind us
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and being rendered in front\Nof us as we move through it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but while it's frozen, morty,\Nwe can get to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, they're over the edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just... as... planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is going to\Nbe such a mindfuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your eyes peeled for the\Ncentral processing room, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how we're gonna\Nscam these idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So, hey, why do these aliens\Nkeep coming after you, Rick,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're so\Nmuch smarter than them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an obsession\Nfor them at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The zigerions have\Nbeen trying to outsmart
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,me for years, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time they do,\NI'm one step ahead of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.16,0:10:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Grab as many processors\Nas you can carry, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys aren't good at much,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but they're real/ygood\Nat making these chips.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Rick: I've got so many,\NI can barely hold them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at... look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops. I dropped one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's plenty of them,\Nyou little goofball.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:10:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, morty! Oh, I gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:10:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, quit it, Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.10,0:11:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing wrong with just a\Nlittle bit of horseplay every
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,now and then, little fella.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. What do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. That was easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Totes malotes, dawg.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kind of hard to believe,\Nyou know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe it, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And once again, I'm flying away\Nwith everything I can carry,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.96,0:11:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and the zigerions\Ngot nothing of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Marklevitz, do you have a...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.93,0:11:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Minute to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.60,0:11:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I'm a fraud.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, let's face it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.81,0:11:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hungry for apples" is just\Na rip-off of "got milk?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost identical.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.19,0:11:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I deserve that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...! Guess...\NI'll just pack up my desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.82,0:11:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. You know what?! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The milk people don't\Nhave a patent on
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,simple rhetorical questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not even a single word\Nin "hungry for apples" that's
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,shared by "got milk?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a completely\Ndifferent slogan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's different!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And I shouldn't be fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be promoted!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes.\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.89,0:12:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes.\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm...\NIt may be derivative,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's the most successful\Ncampaign to come out of this
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.56,0:12:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,agency in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.56,0:12:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not saying it should win\Nan award for commercials,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but it could certainly be\Nnominated for an award
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.15,0:12:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,for commercials specifically\Nabout apples,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,like... an appley or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there really an\Naward called the appley
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,for apple-related ad campaigns?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- Could we nominate me?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be able to use\Nthese processors to make some
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.46,0:12:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,real important science stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:12:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I entered\Nthe code right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha... well, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.06,0:13:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What could this possibly be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it looks like\Nyou're inside a simulation...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside a simulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Game-day bucket go boom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.45,0:13:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, the, uh, doctor's\Nappointment to examine the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,discoloration on your\Nbutthole flaps was -...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Too loud, Cynthia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.62,0:13:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Too loud and too specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We've known how to make\Nconcentrated dark matter
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But now we also know the code to\Nyour fabled safe, Rick Sanchez!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.51,0:13:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All your most valuable\Nsecrets will now be ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah, until I get home\Nbefore you and change the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,combination,\Nyou bunch of idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why you're\Nnever getting home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my god!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I got to tell you, this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even know\Nthis award existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.90,0:14:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm holding one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I want to say that today\Nwas the best day of my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But... the truth is, it's...\NIt's more meaningful than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.87,0:14:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Man: My man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I... am... finally complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My... my... my... my man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.72,0:15:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Jerry?!\N- Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Why are you\Ndressed like a waiter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw it. We don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohhhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.41,0:15:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All: Yes! Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oof!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.86,0:16:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Man up, Jerry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.36,0:16:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I may need you to\Nwork the lasers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man!\NThey're hot on our tail, Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess they really do have\Nconcentrated dark matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know how to make it,\Ntoo, right, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, check the engine room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We just need cesium, plutonic\Nquarks, and bottled water.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all here, Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, morty. Lucky break.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Grab that bucket.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, two parts plutonic quarks,\None part cesium.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.27,0:16:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Uh—huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now empty the water bottle\Ninto the bucket and pour
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it all into the fuel tank so we\Ncan get the hell out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, morty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.78,0:16:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What the -...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:16:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.63,0:17:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my god, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.84,0:17:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How dumb are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're inside a simulation...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Of a simulation...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.43,0:17:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside another giant simulation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.60,0:17:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We never had the recipe for\Nconcentrated dark matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.44,0:17:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But we do now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We do now, sucka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You simulated my\Ngrandson's genitalia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Y—y-you bunch of\Ndiabolical sons of bitches!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.53,0:17:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kevin fought real hard to\Nsupervise that project.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you weren't\Ngonna tell anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never gonna live\Nthis down, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.87,0:17:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Okay.\NAll right, great. Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You win. Can we go home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.79,0:17:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. Can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Show this gullible\Nturd to his shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait. Let me get a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww. Look at his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He's trying to figure out if\Nhe's in a simulation still.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.10,0:18:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a—and, by the way, I don't\Nhave discolored butthole flaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That was part of the simulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sir, should I cancel\Nthat appointment, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Of course you should!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Move it up, actually,\Nif you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Rick:\NHey, Jerry, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if the most meaningful\Nday of your life was a
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.37,0:18:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,simulation operating at\Nminimum capacity?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Those guys took you\Nfor a ride, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You should try having a little\Nrespect for the dummies of the universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,now that you're one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you're right, Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Two parts plutonic quarks...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,One part cesium...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A—and listen,\NI'm sorry for yelling earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I couldn't ask\Nfor a better staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you guys,\Nand I love all your families.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And the final ingredient...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Jerry: Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!\NW-What happened back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.79,0:19:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you ask the smartest\Npeople in the universe, Jerry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They blew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Jerry: So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.21,0:19:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But t-this idea was tested in a\Nstate-of—the—art simulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then, it was\Na terrible simulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, how does a guy like that go\Nhome and have sex with his wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.69,0:20:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, little buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.65,0:20:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,H-H-How you doing\Nin here right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, geez, Rick.\NWhat are you doing, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Y—y-you're a good kid, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Y—you're a real i-little\Nc-character, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.03,0:20:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I had a really\Nrocky road today, m—morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my little friend,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.33,0:20:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We had some good times together,\Nhuh, m-morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We... you're a real\Ntrue hero out in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a ii... you're a real\Ntrooper, huh, m-m-morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been drinking, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.05,0:20:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I really appreciate you, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay, cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.80,0:20:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A-All right, Rick...\NYou little son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Y—y... are you a simulation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.47,0:20:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Are you a simulation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.85,0:20:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.39,0:20:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You little son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I-i-I'm sorry, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Y—you're a good...\NYou're a good kid, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Y—you're a good...\NYou're a good kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.98,0:20:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my god!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.19,0:20:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,W-W-What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.82,0:20:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What a life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:20:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get any of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good-a show!
